  ('ibnmajah', 'The Book of Purification and its Sunnah', 447, '"‏ إِذَا قُمْتَ إِلَى الصَّلاَةِ فَأَسْبِغِ الْوُضُوءَ وَاجْعَلِ الْمَاءَ بَيْنَ أَصَابِعِ يَدَيْكَ وَرِجْلَيْكَ ‏"', NULL, 'It was narrated that Ibn ''Abbas said:''The Messenger of Allah said: ''When you get up for prayer, perform ablution properly and make the water run between your toes and your fingers.''"', 'It was narrated that Ibn ''Abbas said', 'Grade: Hasan (Darussalam)', 'https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:447', 'Sunnah.com developers and open platform data access notice (https://sunnah.com/developers)', TIMESTAMPTZ '2026-04-23T17:38:25.677292Z'),
  ('ibnmajah', 'The Book of Purification and its Sunnah', 448, '"‏ أَسْبِغِ الْوُضُوءَ وَخَلِّلْ بَيْنَ الأَصَابِعِ ‏"', NULL, '''Asim bin Laqit bin Saabirah narrated that his father said:"The Messenger of Allah said: perform ablution properly and let the water run between your fingers."', '''Asim bin Laqit bin Saabirah narrated that his father said', 'Grade: Sahih (Darussalam)', 'https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:448', 'Sunnah.com developers and open platform data access notice (https://sunnah.com/developers)', TIMESTAMPTZ '2026-04-23T17:38:25.677292Z'),
  ('ibnmajah', 'The Book of Purification and its Sunnah', 449, 'حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الْمَلِكِ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ الرَّقَاشِيُّ، حَدَّثَنَا مَعْمَرُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عُبَيْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ أَبِي رَافِعٍ، حَدَّثَنِي أَبِي، عَنْ عُبَيْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ أَبِي رَافِعٍ، عَنْ أَبِيهِ، أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ ـ صلى الله عليه وسلم ـ كَانَ إِذَا تَوَضَّأَ حَرَّكَ خَاتَمَهُ ‏.‏', NULL, '''Ubaidullah bin Abu Rafi'' narrated from his father that:Whenever the Messenger of Allah performed ablution, he moved his ring.', '''Ubaidullah bin Abu Rafi'' narrated from his father that', 'Grade: Da''if (Darussalam)', 'https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:449', 'Sunnah.com developers and open platform data access notice (https://sunnah.com/developers)', TIMESTAMPTZ '2026-04-23T17:38:25.677292Z'),
  ('ibnmajah', 'The Book of Purification and its Sunnah', 450, '"‏ وَيْلٌ لِلأَعْقَابِ مِنَ النَّارِ أَسْبِغُوا الْوُضُوءَ ‏"', NULL, '''Abdullah bin ''Amr said:"The Messenger of Allah saw some people performing ablution, and their heels were dry. He said: ''Woe to the heels because of Hell-fire, perform ablution properly!''"', '''Abdullah bin ''Amr said', 'Grade: Sahih (Darussalam)', 'https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:450', 'Sunnah.com developers and open platform data access notice (https://sunnah.com/developers)', TIMESTAMPTZ '2026-04-23T17:38:25.677292Z'),
  ('ibnmajah', 'The Book of Purification and its Sunnah', 451, '"‏ وَيْلٌ لِلأَعْقَابِ مِنَ النَّارِ ‏"', NULL, 'It was narrated that ''Aishah said:The Messenger of Allah said: ''Woe to the heels because of Hell-fire.''"', 'It was narrated that ''Aishah said', 'Grade: Sahih (Darussalam)', 'https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:451', 'Sunnah.com developers and open platform data access notice (https://sunnah.com/developers)', TIMESTAMPTZ '2026-04-23T17:38:25.677292Z'),
